trans-unit.source: Indicates when events and other life-cycle events occur while a <xref href="System.Web.HttpApplication"></xref> request is being processed.

The RequestNotification enumeration is used with the <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.CurrentNotification%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.HttpContext> class to determine what event in the pipeline is currently processing.

To determine when all the handlers for a specific event of the <xref:System.Web.HttpApplication> instance have finished processing, use the <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.IsPostNotification%2A> property.
The RequestNotification type is introduced in the [!INCLUDE[net_v35_long](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].
For more information, see [Versions and Dependencies](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
Indicates that the <xref href="System.Web.HttpApplication.AcquireRequestState"></xref> event was raised for the request and is processing.
To be added.
Indicates that the <xref href="System.Web.HttpApplication.AuthenticateRequest"></xref> event was raised for the request and is processing.
To be added.
Indicates that the <xref href="System.Web.HttpApplication.AuthorizeRequest"></xref> event was raised for the request and is processing.
To be added.
Indicates that the <xref href="System.Web.HttpApplication.BeginRequest"></xref> event was raised for the request and is processing.
To be added.
Indicates that the <xref href="System.Web.HttpApplication.EndRequest"></xref> event was raised for the request and is processing.
To be added.
Indicates that the handler that is mapped to the requested resource is being invoked to process the request.
To be added.
Indicates that the <xref href="System.Web.HttpApplication.LogRequest"></xref> event was raised for the request and is processing.
To be added.
Indicates that the <xref href="System.Web.HttpApplication.MapRequestHandler"></xref> event was raised for the request and is processing.
To be added.
Indicates a point in the application life cycle just before the handler that processes the request is mapped.
To be added.
Indicates that the <xref href="System.Web.HttpApplication.ReleaseRequestState"></xref> event was raised for the request and is processing.
To be added.
Indicates that the <xref href="System.Web.HttpApplication.ResolveRequestCache"></xref> event was raised for the request and is processing.
To be added.
Indicates that processing of the request is complete and that the response is being sent.
To be added.
Indicates that the <xref href="System.Web.HttpApplication.UpdateRequestCache"></xref> event was raised for the request and is processing.
To be added.
